name: Rakuten Technology Page
body:
### Welcome To Rakuten Technology Pages

The following is a list of Rakuten Group supported open source projects.

* Rakuten https://github.com/rakutentech
  * Rakuten Web Service
    * https://github.com/rakuten-ws/
    * http://webservice.rakuten.co.jp/sdk/
  * LeoFS 
    * https://github.com/leo-project/leofs
    * http://leo-project.net/leofs/
  * ROMA
    * https://github.com/roma/roma
  * Egison
    * https://github.com/egison/egison
    * http://www.egison.org/
  * Fairy
    * https://code.google.com/p/fairy-prj/
  * RakutenMA
    * https://github.com/rakuten-nlp/rakutenma
* Kobo https://github.com/kobolabs
* Wuakitv https://github.com/wuakitv
* Viki https://github.com/viki-org

Rakuten programmers have been contributing the following projects. (not complete list)
* https://github.com/XSecurity/XSecurity
  * http://www.slideshare.net/rakutentech/extend-security-on-xcode
* http://cockatoo.jp/wiki2/main
* https://github.com/hbase-sculptor/sculptor
* Cassandra
* MongoDB
* OpenStack

### Contact
Please contact dev-pr@mail.rakuten.com if you have any questions.
